FastAPI is a modern, fast web framework for building APIs with Python 3.7+.

It is designed to be easy to use and highly efficient. FastAPI is built on top of Starlette for the web parts and Pydantic for data validation.

Some key features of FastAPI include:
- Fast performance, comparable to Node.js and Go
- Automatic interactive API documentation using Swagger UI
- Easy request validation using Python type hints
- Asynchronous support using async and await

FastAPI is widely used for building RESTful APIs, microservices, and backend systems for web and mobile applications.

